description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Try and breed each of the fish in this addictive game, but watch out! Some fish have special abilities that can cause chaos in your tank! You'll have to manage your money and your fish to breed them all, from the Guppies right up to the Cod Father.
